Suggests: knitr, markdown, rmarkdown, testthat, mvtnorm, covr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0-7), disordR (>= 0.9-8-2), methods, Rdpack
LinkingTo: Rcpp
URL: https://github.com/RobinHankin/evitaicossa
